graph TD
    Query[User Query] --> Embed[Embedding Model]
    Embed --> PV[Pinecone Search<br/>Recall Top-K]
    PV -->|Candidate Docs| RR[Cohere Rerank<br/>Precision Scoring]
    RR -->|Re-ordered Top-3| Judge[Context Pruning]
    Judge -->|Final Context| LLM[Bedrock Model]
    
    subgraph "Phase 1: Recall"
    PV
    end
    
    subgraph "Phase 2: Rerank"
    RR
    end
    
    subgraph "Phase 3: Generation"
    LLM
    end
